PREVIEW AND DEBUG
PREVIEW MODE
Click "Preview" in GTM Enter site URL GTM debug panel opens at bottom 
What to check: 
Tags fired on this event Tags not fired (and why) Variables and their values Data layer contents 
DEBUG TIPS
Tag not firing: 
Check TCs Verify data layer push Check tag sequencing 
Wrong variable value: 
Check data layer structure Verify variable path (nested objects) Check timing (data may not exist yet) 
Multiple firings: 
Check trigger uniqueness Look for duplicate tags Check tag firing options 
--- 
WORKSPACES AND VERSIONING
WORKSPACES
Use workspaces for team collaboration: 
Default workspace for production Separate workspaces for large changes Merge when ready 
VERSION MANAGEMENT
Best practices: 
Name every version descriptively Add notes explaining changes Review changes before publish Keep production version noted 
