ADVANCED PATTERNS
TAG SEQUENCING
Setup tags to fire in order: Tag Configuration Advanced Settings Tag Sequencing 
Use cases: 
Config tag before event tags Pixel initialization before tracking Cleanup after conversion 
EXCEPTION HANDLING
Trigger exceptions - Prevent tag from firing: 
Exclude certain pages Exclude internal traffic Exclude during testing 
